{"tid":24421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"就到聖誕！ 基層家庭夢想食聖誕大餐","createTime":"2016-12-05T13:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T05:01:19.000Z","uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aef492457b3d8c7ca803433c6db98cefaa4fea33","tid":24421,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i40.tinypic.com/2lo6n1g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi40.tinypic.com%2F2lo6n1g.jpg&h=acdfb593&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.littleoslo.com/cnt/home/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/winner-612x920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.littleoslo.com%2Fcnt%2Fhome%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F12%2Fwinner-612x920.jpg&h=0481e142&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明報專訊】繼去年明益你「夢想成真」，為兩名讀者達成心願後，今年聖誕我們繼續送暖，為讀者陳先生一家實現聖誕願望：「15年來，幾乎從沒帶兒子外出食聖誕大餐，希望給兒子一個特別難忘的聖誕。」表面看來，陳家跟一般小康之家無異，卻又背負?多個不足為外人道的重擔，這是現時不少中產家庭的寫照。生活從來不易，總是一闊三大，尤其在佳節舉家外出食餐好，對不少家庭來說還是個付不起的夢想。明益你聯同The <br />\nMira酒店，為陳家於今年聖誕節送上免費自助晚餐，讓他們為2011年畫上圓滿的句號。 <br />\n<br />\n陳基棠先生任職銀行電腦部 System Manager，太太是認證機構秘書，育有一名中四兒子，是不折不扣的小康之家，但背負的生活重擔，往往讓陳先生慨嘆「錢總是不知所終」。兩人正供養三個老人家，由於兩人均在職，需請家傭照顧；又為兒子請來兩名補習老師，加上學習長笛及參加童軍活動，都是陳家重要支出。 <br />\n<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">最大的負擔，莫過於供一層位於港島東的七百多呎自住單位，佔收入約三分之一，即使三口之家月入數萬元</span>，七除八扣後還是所剩無幾，實在是啞子吃黃蓮。難怪精打細算的陳太表示，每年最多只能與兒子食自助餐一兩次，並選擇價錢較低廉的午餐時段，至於較平時貴幾成的聖誕大餐，對他們一家來說是過於奢侈的消費：「一家三口連車費，動輒數千。」 <br />\n<br />\n夾心中產「有苦說不清」 <br />\n<br />\n因此每年聖誕，陳家都與親友在家搞派對，親身下廚以減低開支。但兒子畢竟已15歲，陳生還是希望能讓他一嘗在聖誕樹和熱鬧的節日氣氛下，享受一頓豐富大餐，令兒子有個幸福難忘的回憶，於是便去信明益你參加「夢想成真」活動，寫上這個心願。 <br />\n<br />\n「知道獲選後，第一時間告訴兒子，他還不斷跟身邊朋友說今年聖誕要出尖沙嘴食buffet呢。」看兒子首次坐在聖誕樹下，享受自助餐盛宴而展現出燦爛笑容，應該是陳生陳太今年最好的聖誕及新年禮物吧！"},{"pid":"d997cc2ae870b197a1fbd5916bf20407e6382637","tid":24421,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:52:07.000Z","msg":"有苦說不清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">工人 供樓 2個補習老師  學樂器<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\">依家話冇錢食自助餐</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3206f4b7612a5da9884d2db6d89d1d7abc14f79e","tid":24421,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔學咁多野唔供樓咪餐餐食buffet囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b726c036b8d4f9427fe62e4779596c387dc850","tid":24421,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有苦說不清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">工人 供樓 2個補習老師  學樂器<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\">依家話冇錢食自助餐</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n薯片佬先係中產"},{"pid":"4a598ca8bd64b58fd1aea5648c4c26272cce7b5c","tid":24421,"uid":3460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"人地唔使養樓咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src